    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    CARTOONISH COLOR PALETTE
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    
    Design Philosophy:
    - Bright, saturated colors with playful energy
    - High contrast for readability (WCAG AA compliant)
    - Bold primary colors with fun accent pops
    - Soft shadows and highlights for depth
    
    Color Contrast Ratios (against white #FFFFFF):
    - Primary (#FF6B6B): 3.94:1 - Use with white text ✓
    - Secondary (#4ECDC4): 2.52:1 - Use with dark text
    - Accent (#FFE66D): 1.54:1 - Use with dark text only
    - Text Primary (#2D3436): 15.5:1 - Excellent readability ✓
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    -->

